ials can be disabled by clicking the button again.\n    \u2022 Zoom button is now pressure-sensitive for more precise zoom.\n    \u2022 Zoom settings and gimbal tilt reset before spawning a new drone.\n    \u2022 Adjusted medal times.\n    \u2022 Sharper rendering of texts and Images.\n    \u2022 Active control mode displayed in the \"Controls Info\" window.\n    \u2022 Improved render performance for Meta Quest Pro.\nUSER AREA ENHANCEMENTS:\n    \u2022 Dynamic leaderboard for comparing results with other users and friends.\n      Added tutorial screen for the photospots", "created_date": 1735487689, "id": "28098457163103525", "version": "1.7.0", "version_code": 10700, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5294103097298922", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28098457163103525"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1735215719, "id": "28068980212717887", "version": "1.6.43", "version_code": 10643, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5294103097298922", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28098457163103525"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "353607312647721"}]}, "change_log": "Leaderboards and Achievements", "created_date": 1728409